snippet.title: F-Zero Pocket - Quick Race (Mute City I)
snippet.description:
A quick showcase of my newly released fangame F-Zero Pocket, a tribute to the almost 30-year old series and to the GameBoy Color.


In this short video I do a simple race in the first track of the race, Mute City I, playing as Jody Summers.


Download the game: https://linky439.itch.io/f-zero-pocket
Twitter account: https://twitter.com/Linky439
